g.title: LThis ongoing research work is developed at the German Research Center for Artificial Intelligence (Deutsches Forschungszentrum für Künstliche Intelligenz (DFKI) GmbH). It is work in progress and presents a purchase-to-pay ontology and vocabulary for describing purchase-to-pay processes and electronic invoices. It reuses parts of the European Standard EN 16931-1.|Language: en
